Class NamedElasticsearchAnalyzerReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.search.analyzer.impl.RemoteAnalyzerReference

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, AnalyzerReference
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NamedElasticsearch2NormalizerReference, NamedElasticsearch52NormalizerReference

    public class NamedElasticsearchAnalyzerReference
extends ElasticsearchAnalyzerReference
    A reference to an Elasticsearch analyzer that also provides a name for this analyzer.

    Such a reference may initially only contain the analyzer name, but in this case it will be fully initialized with the actual analyzer later.

    Author:
    Yoann Rodiere
